# Code-health reports: commit the consolidated markdown reports ONLY.
# Raw per-tool output (jscpd JSON, semgrep JSON, eslint JSON, gitleaks JSON,
# knip logs, etc.) is noisy/large and lives under
# ridgetopai-reports/code-health/<date>/raw/ (outside this repo) by default.
# This guard makes sure that if anyone ever points REPORT_ROOT inside the repo,
# the raw dumps still never get committed.
raw/
*/raw/
*.json
*.log
!code-health-*.md
